  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design The Perfect Maze</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Circuit Maze</strong> is a tower defense game without the combat. Your goal is to build the longest possible maze with the  resources you are given on each level. Find the most optimized maze layouts across 80 handcrafted  levels, where you need to utilise each block to its fullest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creativity and careful planning are both a must if you want to become a master maze builder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Circuit Maze </strong>is a relaxed experience without any stressful elements, giving you the time you need to plan out your perfect solution to each of the challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.poster.avif?t=1750594399\" width=350 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.webm?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.mp4?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower defense style building gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 handcrafted and challenging levels that will put your maze building skills to the test.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of building blocks. Design the perfect maze layout to get the most out of each special block's unique features.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing but challenging gameplay. No stressful elements, giving you the time you need to find the perfect solution for each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.poster.avif?t=1750594399\" width=400 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.webm?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.mp4?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Good Luck & Happy Mazing!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design The Perfect Maze</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Circuit Maze</strong> is a tower defense game without the combat. Your goal is to build the longest possible maze with the  resources you are given on each level. Find the most optimized maze layouts across 80 handcrafted  levels, where you need to utilise each block to its fullest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creativity and careful planning are both a must if you want to become a master maze builder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Circuit Maze </strong>is a relaxed experience without any stressful elements, giving you the time you need to plan out your perfect solution to each of the challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.poster.avif?t=1750594399\" width=350 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.webm?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b4c54797bcf3fb40a04d186db37e78b3.mp4?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower defense style building gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 handcrafted and challenging levels that will put your maze building skills to the test.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of building blocks. Design the perfect maze layout to get the most out of each special block's unique features.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing but challenging gameplay. No stressful elements, giving you the time you need to find the perfect solution for each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.poster.avif?t=1750594399\" width=400 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.webm?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421850/extras/b00c2c8ede3474bb1ab1391f4e754d60.mp4?t=1750594399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Good Luck & Happy Mazing!</i></p>",
